title: Come To Your Senses (Tim Somers)
description:
Your doubts don’t disqualify you. 

In “Come To Your Senses,” Elevation Church’s Youth Pastor, Tim Somers, reveals to us that, when we’re facing doubt in the present, we must remember how God remained faithful in the past.

If you’ve just made a decision for Christ, please respond HERE: http://ele.vc/tIepfr
